{"1350200":{"success":true,"data":{"type":"game","name":"IMMORTALITY","steam_appid":1350200,"required_age":0,"is_free":false,"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"Match cut your own path through the footage and solve the mystery: <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1350200\/extras\/b1275271bd402c6c6366674511939a0c.webp?t=1724989848\" width=640 height=36 \/><\/span><br><br>IMMORTALITY is an interactive trilogy from Sam Barlow, creator of <i>Her Story<\/i>. Use the cinematic ability to teleport from scene to scene to explore a treasure trove of newly unearthed footage from the three lost films of Marissa Marcel and traverse decades of movie history:<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1350200\/extras\/bf338bb9bcd01f42a64b9cac94f63e1c.webp?t=1724989848\" width=80 height=27 \/><\/span><br>Alan Fischer directs <i>Ambrosio<\/i> his adaptation of M. G. Lewis’s notorious Gothic novel <i>The Monk<\/i>. He casts unknown Marissa Marcel as the infamous Matilda.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1350200\/extras\/0d310a7ae935477f626318b4f5b01eac.avif?t=1724989848\" width=640 height=240 \/><\/span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1350200\/extras\/6bba83ab06238b446f65f6b906c3f2f6.webp?t=1724989848\" width=80 height=27 \/><\/span><br>John Durick writes his thriller <i>Minsky<\/i> with Marcel in mind. Set in New York City, the movie concerns the death of a famous artist and Marissa stars as the muse suspected of murdering him.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1350200\/extras\/3584681b4e257f25302e0aa225fe86d3.avif?t=1724989848\" width=640 height=240 \/><\/span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1350200\/extras\/9ce6ed17ad6766f74175ed1585f89445.webp?t=1724989848\" width=80 height=27 \/><\/span><br>For his swansong, Durick teams up with Marcel again as she returns from a lengthy hiatus. The movie <i>Two of Everything<\/i> is a subversive thriller which explores the duality between a successful pop star and her body double. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1350200\/extras\/5d3c5d9a4aed11ac94c2cbb413c66c21.avif?t=1724989848\" width=640 height=240 \/><\/span><br><br>None of these movies was ever released. They were thought to be lost or destroyed. Until now.","about_the_game":"Match cut your own path through the footage and solve the mystery: <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1350200\/extras\/b1275271bd402c6c6366674511939a0c.webp?t=1724989848\" width=640 height=36 \/><\/span><br><br>IMMORTALITY is an interactive trilogy from Sam Barlow, creator of <i>Her Story<\/i>. Use the cinematic ability to teleport from scene to scene to explore a treasure trove of newly unearthed footage from the three lost films of Marissa Marcel and traverse decades of movie history:<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1350200\/extras\/bf338bb9bcd01f42a64b9cac94f63e1c.webp?t=1724989848\" width=80 height=27 \/><\/span><br>Alan Fischer directs <i>Ambrosio<\/i> his adaptation of M. G. Lewis’s notorious Gothic novel <i>The Monk<\/i>. He casts unknown Marissa Marcel as the infamous Matilda.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1350200\/extras\/0d310a7ae935477f626318b4f5b01eac.avif?t=1724989848\" width=640 height=240 \/><\/span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1350200\/extras\/6bba83ab06238b446f65f6b906c3f2f6.webp?t=1724989848\" width=80 height=27 \/><\/span><br>John Durick writes his thriller <i>Minsky<\/i> with Marcel in mind. Set in New York City, the movie concerns the death of a famous artist and Marissa stars as the muse suspected of murdering him.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1350200\/extras\/3584681b4e257f25302e0aa225fe86d3.avif?t=1724989848\" width=640 height=240 \/><\/span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1350200\/extras\/9ce6ed17ad6766f74175ed1585f89445.webp?t=1724989848\" width=80 height=27 \/><\/span><br>For his swansong, Durick teams up with Marcel again as she returns from a lengthy hiatus. The movie <i>Two of Everything<\/i> is a subversive thriller which explores the duality between a successful pop star and her body double. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1350200\/extras\/5d3c5d9a4aed11ac94c2cbb413c66c21.avif?t=1724989848\" width=640 height=240 \/><\/span><br><br>None of these movies was ever released. They were thought to be lost or destroyed. Until now.","short_description":"Marissa Marcel was a film star. She made three movies. But none of the movies were ever released. And Marissa Marcel disappeared. An interactive trilogy from Sam Barlow, creator of Her Story.","supported_languages":"English, French, Italian, German, Spanish - Spain, Japanese, Korean, Portuguese - Brazil, Spanish - Latin America, Arabic, Polis